column1: Title  : M601661 - Food & Beverage Services Index, (2017 = 100), At Current Prices, (SSIC 2015 Version 2018), Monthly
Cafes, Food Courts & Other Eating Places *
Food & beverage services refers to the sales of prepared food and drinks for in-premises consumption or on a take-away basis.  All eating places are included except hawker stalls.
CAFES, FOOD COURTS & OTHER EATING PLACES - FROM JANUARY 2005, DATA EXCLUDES FOOD CATERERS.
